	<br/>
	<br/><font color='#FF7F00'>CSAT Headquarters</font>
    <br/>Capture and secure the CSAT Headquarters within Doodstil. This facility houses a barracks and serves as a vital command and control centre for enemy forces in the region. Capturing the headquarters will significantly undermine CSAT's ability to resist further NATO advancements in the area.
	<br/>
	<br/>%1 <!--- Casualties Cap --->
	<br/><font size='18' color='#80FF00'>CREDITS</font>
	<br/>Created by <font color='#FF0080'>2600K</font color>
